	* scm/siscweb/graphviz.scm:
	error checking for invalid layout and format parameters; reordered
	mime-type list

	* scm/siscweb/html.scm:
	malformed html now causes error; #f element is now ignored for
	handyness' sake; graphviz image map now fails silently

	* scm/sxml/dotml.scm:
	sub-graph rank needs not be a symbol anymore; now errors out in case
	of bad dotml

2005-07-06  acolomba@@snoopy.local  <acolomba@@snoopy>

